title: Stop, look & rent! Call Newberry Square today!
posting_body: Newberry Square Apartments is an urban village set in a convenient and tranquil environment right outside of Seattle in Lynnwood, WA.

Our studio, one, two and three bedroom apartment homes come standard with gorgeous gourmet kitchens, stainless steel appliances, spacious living rooms, and walk-in closets— all of which make it easy for you to settle right into your new home.
